snippet.title: Dragon Ball FighterZ - XB1/PS4/PC - Vegito Character Intro
snippet.description:
Vegito (SSGSS) is coming in less than 10 days! Clashes with Zamasu (Fused) are going to be epic! 
Who will you side with? #teamvegito or #Teamzamasu ?
Both Zamasu (Fused) and Vegito (SSGSS) DLC will be available on the 31st of May as stand-alone and in the FighterZ Pass.
